  "status": "Final",
  "summary": "This standard is an extension of [ERC-721](./eip-721.md). It separates the holding right and transfer right of non-fungible tokens (NFTs) and Soulbound Tokens (SBTs) and defines a new role, `guard` with `expires`. The flexibility of the `guard` setting enables the design of NFT anti-theft, NFT lending, NFT leasing, SBT, etc.",
  "title": "Guard of NFT/SBT, an Extension of ERC-721"
